OL,3,CNewcastle man handed suspended
OL,4,Csentence over offensive tweets
OL,6,FA Newcastle man has been handed a 16-
OL,7,Fmonth suspended sentence after posting
OL,8,Foffensive tweets.
OL,10,FNathan Thompson, aged 25, of Whickham
OL,11,FView, Newcastle, pleaded guilty to six
OL,12,Foffences of inciting racial hatred and
OL,13,Ftwo offences of malicious
OL,14,Fcommunications at Newcastle Crown
OL,15,FCourt in March.
OL,17,FIt follows Counter Terrorism Policing
OL,18,Fidentifying two X (formerly Twitter)
OL,19,Faccounts which were sharing extreme
OL,20,Fright wing, racist, antisemitic, and
OL,21,Ftransphobic content.
