OL,3,CNewcastle man handed suspended
OL,4,Csentence over offensive tweets
OL,6,FThe Court heard how Thompson had
OL,7,Fshared or reposted offensive, extreme
OL,8,Fright-wing messages about black and
OL,9,Fbrown people, Jews, Muslims, refugees,
OL,10,Fimmigrants and members of the LGBT
OL,11,Fcommunity.
OL,13,FThe accounts used by Thompson were
OL,14,Fvisible to the public and also shared
OL,15,Fsupport for those who have carried out
OL,16,Fterror attacks in the past.
OL,18,FThe accounts were traced back to
OL,19,FThompson, leading to his arrest in
OL,20,FJuly 2023.
