OL,3,CNewcastle man handed suspended
OL,4,Csentence over offensive tweets
OL,6,FEnquiries traced the accounts back to
OL,7,FThompson, which resulted in Counter
OL,8,FTerrorism Policing North East
OL,9,Farresting him in July 2023.
OL,11,FIn interview following his arrest,
OL,12,FThompson accepted responsibility for
OL,13,Fboth offending Twitter accounts.
OL,15,FIn sentencing Judge Clemitson told
OL,16,FThompson his posts celebrated Hitler
OL,17,Fand his actions and fascism. She added
OL,18,Fthat the messages dehumanised refugees
OL,19,Fand people from non-white ethnic
OL,20,Fgroups.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G3/6
