OL,4,Csentence over offensive tweets
OL,6,FThey also depicted deliberately
OL,7,Foffensive images such as the Qur'an
OL,8,Fbeing burned, she added.
OL,10,FShe said: "Each homophobic,
OL,11,Ftransphobic, Islamophobic,
OL,12,Fantisemitic, racist or fascist tweet
OL,13,Ffans the flames of division and
OL,14,Fhatred."
OL,16,FBut she did not impose an immediate
OL,17,Fcustodial sentence, adding Thompson
OL,18,Fhad "borderline" learning difficulties
OL,19,Fand was 'isolated', spending a great
OL,20,Fdeal of time in his bedroom on his
OL,21,Fcomputer.
